{"tid":26879,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樂視告急】賈躍亭押股疑遭斬倉 樂視突停牌！","createTime":"2016-12-07T03:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T04:45:53.000Z","uid":54517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5edea9c24fa8c4f06617d330d166139af6cbd592","tid":26879,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:42:46.000Z","msg":"樂視近日屢傳壞消息，其於深圳上市的樂視網昨日尾市更重挫接近跌停，今早樂視網卻突然於開市前停牌，擬披露重大事項。<br />\n<br />\n樂視網昨日尾市突然急插，一度低見35.01元人民幣，收市仍錄得7.85%的跌幅。其後有內媒報道指，創辦人兼行政總裁賈躍亭有一筆樂視網股權質押貸款的強制平倉線為35.21元人民幣，質押總計5.07億股，佔賈躍亭持股比例高達64.81%，而樂視網昨日一度跌破該筆股權質押的平倉線，懷疑因該批股份遭強制斬倉，導致股價一瀉如注。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，樂視近期多次傳出爆煲消息，有外國媒體更形容其電動車項目猶如龐氏騙局，昨日又再傳出，樂視體育內部已決定整體裁員20%，其中智能硬件部將裁員50%，估計整個樂視體育將有200員工面臨被裁；而樂視體育總編輯敖銘已提交請辭，即將離職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1481075281580&amp;issue=20161207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1481075281580%26issue%3D20161207&d=bacUdPQdmd0OO3KQZ1uWsYscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=3b2e7c15\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1481075281580&amp;issue=20161207</a>"},{"pid":"c55238d700980f8b664db527df793eaeb7bd6a6d","tid":26879,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:44:38.000Z","msg":"抵能死啊。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063c8fa4e6128c24676412a718159acfa3d628a1","tid":26879,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:45:19.000Z","msg":"支爆近了"},{"pid":"366a45d7a55803824b71befde2c8af65bbbc7413","tid":26879,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:50:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支爆近了</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c413e4810bafef2ac2e593e163af5c47f796e3f","tid":26879,"uid":53411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T04:00:34.000Z","msg":"猶如龐氏騙局<br />\n下下